video_type.reasoning: Live street approaches with openers, number exchanges, and post-approach commentary. Title confirms '3 Girls In 10 minutes'.

SPEAKER_00.reasoning: mixed_diarization_error: Primarily the coach (delivers all openers, compliments, camera commentary, number close logistics), but also contains target responses in conversations 2 and 3 — e.g. 'Thank you' at segments 94/96, 'You too' at 134, and other short responses that are clearly from the women being approached.

SPEAKER_01.reasoning: mixed_diarization_error: Primarily Target 1 (Hungarian woman in conversation 1 — gives short responses, speaks Hungarian, provides contact info), but also appears as Target 3 in conversation 3 (segments 120-121, 169, 171-172, 189) which is a different woman. Two different targets merged into one speaker ID.

SPEAKER_02.reasoning: Target in conversations 2 and 3 — gives short responses to questions, provides personal info when asked (studies medicine, lives in neighborhood), reacts to coach's compliments and proposals.

UNKNOWN.reasoning: Only 2 segments — segment 174 ('Uh-uh') could be target 3 responding to religious question, segment 233 ('We'll see you next time') could be outro/other voice.
